### Health Check
GET http://localhost:8082/health

### Get System Metrics
GET http://localhost:8082/api/v1/metrics

### Get Queue Status
GET http://localhost:8082/api/v1/queue/status

### Get Next Task (no filter)
GET http://localhost:8082/api/v1/queue/next

### Get Next Task (with repo filter)
GET http://localhost:8082/api/v1/queue/next?repo_id=/test/repo

### Cancel a Task
POST http://localhost:8082/api/v1/tasks/cancel
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "task_id": "task-123",
  "reason": "Manual cancellation for testing"
}
